## Jaddangi AI Lab - Glass Box Architecture

Built with ❤️ by Kurumalla Venkataramana
Jaddangi IT & AI Consultancy
https://github.com/venkatramanakurumalla/jaddangi-ai-lab

This project implements a pure PyTorch transformer architecture inspired by:
- Qwen2 (Alibaba Cloud)
- LLaMA (Meta)
- Attention Is All You Need (Vaswani et al.)
- Rotary Position Embeddings (Su et al.)
- LoRA: Low-Rank Adaptation (Hu et al.)

All research papers and implementations are properly attributed.
